&lt;li&gt;Clean and maintain kitchen areas, dishes, and equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operate commercial kitchen equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stock supplies, monitor inventory, and receive deliveries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow recipes, portion control, and nutrition guidelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain food safety logs and documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
